description	"Mara Jade

Class Summary: 
A Sith/pistoleer hybrid that rewards flanking, skirmishing, and swapping between weapons and force powers.

Lightsaber
- Can use Blue and Yellow Styles
- Deflect (2)
- Defense 2
- Passively regenerates BP even when running/jumping
- No extra BP drain on jumps

Weaponry:
- Pistol (3)
- Sonic Grenade (1)
- Frag Grenade (1)
  
Force Powers:
- Jump (3)
- Push (2)
- Pull (3)
- Sense (2)
- Speed (1)
- Lightning (2)
- Force Block (2)
- Force Focus (1)

Attributes:
- Invisible to force sight
- Invulnerable to Mind Trick
- Flipkick

Mara Jade was raised as a servant and assassin to Emperor Palpatine and became a high-level Force-using operative. After Palpatine's death, she received his last command, which was to kill Luke Skywalker; however, the death of her Master caused her to go rogue."